==English==

===Verb===
'''[[stick]] [[out]] [[like]] a [[sore]] [[thumb]]'''

# {{idiom}} Be very noticeably [[different]], especially in a negative way; to be particularly [[obtrusive]], [[conspicuous]], [[blatant]], or [[prominent]]; to attract undue [[attention]] or [[notice]].
#:''With that guilty smile of his, he '''stuck out like a sore thumb'''.''